ike":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:58:49.000Z","msg":"自已出身咁就讀好d 書啦"},{"pid":"25fafad6d8ce7dc60f142215deb6a885ab725b69","tid":904830,"uid":8336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T06:01:14.000Z","msg":"巴打，祝你以後有個好嘅人生"},{"pid":"fab9d3525bd9876ab9e7b9ee16b86637d761e595","tid":904830,"uid":192754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"嘗試由尾睇上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f1ff041f459f6db9aedcf75a340908bf9c4983","tid":904830,"uid":222523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dacfdadce835b74887866c68b72bc1be1fd3eeb","tid":904830,"uid":198163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:32:28.000Z","msg":"有個fd 同你差唔多情怳 聽你講完我明佢點諗了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"估唔到有人同我差唔多 多啲支持佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d706fc220cd803f21b9548f973e1ef27b401321","tid":904830,"uid":222523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baa336b8452499f44320655ee6697b7f2ed9e683","tid":904830,"uid":198163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:32:49.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:03:01.000Z","msg":"感激！"},{"pid":"60255bffeb4bf8b9cd83d5fc9f0af7fcd71b4e62","tid":904830,"uid":222523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a491b868672ee63b3bada7e56fe3f613ec830b7","tid":904830,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"結論：窮人唔好生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:04:35.000Z","msg":"其實唔係唔可以生既 只係生前真係要好好考慮清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f13b77d23e4971e2a434a9f1c726655abded079"